Package: MethylPipe
Type: Package
Title: Downstream preprocessing pipeline for cfRRBS starting from Bismark coverage
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Luca","Visser",email="Luca.Visser@UGent.be",role=c("aut","cre"))
Description: Read Bismark coverage files and run standardized downstream preprocessing: filtering, aggregation to regions, Beta/M conversions, PCA/UMAP/t-SNE, batch checks and correction, QC reporting, and export for modelling.
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
